In order to build remv you need the boost libraries installed (see boost.org).
remv has been tested on linux with boost >= 1.37
remv will not compile with boost earlier than 1.36.

To compile and install run
./configure
make
make install

For configure options run configure --help.

See the man page for description.

Tested on
    - amd64 freebsd 7.2 gcc-4.1.2, gcc-4.2.1
    - x86_64 linux 2.6.30-gentoo-r4, 2.6.33-gentoo-r2, gcc-4.4.1, gcc Gentoo 4.4.3-r2

